-- Mosaic CEO Says Availability of Labor ‘A Real Challenge’
-- B y   S i m o n   C a s e y
-- 2012-01-27T16:02:11Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-27/mosaic-ceo-says-availability-of-labor-a-real-challenge-.html
Mosaic Co. (MOS)  Chief Executive Officer
Jim Prokopanko said hiring workers in western  Canada  is a “real
challenge” as the fertilizer producer has to compete with
energy companies in the region.  “It’s a gold-rush, boomtown mentality going on,” he said
today in an interview with Bloomberg Television’s  Erik Schatzker 
at the  World Economic Forum ’s annual meeting in Davos,
 Switzerland .  To contact the reporter on this story:
